---
title: How to
blog: travel_articles
---
<main>

<section class="section--introduction bg-gray-light text-blue-dark px-4">
  <div class="container mx-auto xl:px-32 xxl:px-48 pt-12">
    <p class="text-xl xl:text-3xl mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-tight">Pledging not to fly can seem daunting if you don't know where to start. Our 'how to' articles can help you get cracking, with <a href="#destination-inspiration" class="underline underline-orange hover:text-orange">ideas for travel destinations</a>, and everything from <a href="https://flightfree.co.uk/post/going-with-children-by-train/" class="underline underline-orange hover:text-orange">tips on travelling with children</a>, to guidance on <a href="https://flightfree.co.uk/post/tips-on-talking-about-a-socially-awkward-topic/" class="underline underline-orange hover:text-orange">how to talk to the people around you</a>  about your pledge.</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4 md:mb-10">How to</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto xl:px-32 xxl:px-48 pb-12">
    <ul class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-2 xl:gap-4 ff-bullets">
      <%- data.how_to_links.primary.links.each do |link| -%>
      <li class="px-2 md:px-0 py-1 sm:py-2 md:py-0 flex items-center"><span class="inline-block mr-1"><%= partial "svg/dot_pink.svg" %></span><a href="<%= link.url %>" class="ml-1 md:ml-4 text-xl xl:text-3xl hover:text-orange"><%= link.text %></a></li>
      <%- end -%>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto xl:px-32 xxl:px-48">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4 md:mb-10">How to travel</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto xl:px-32 xxl:px-48 pb-12">
    <ul class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-2 xl:gap-4 ff-bullets">
      <%- data.how_to_links.secondary.links.each do |link| -%>
      <li class="px-2 md:px-0 py-1 sm:py-2 md:py-0 flex items-center"><span class="inline-block mr-1"><%= partial "svg/dot_blue.svg" %></span><a href="<%= link.url %>" class="ml-1 md:ml-4 text-xl xl:text-3xl hover:text-orange"><%= link.text %></a></li>
      <%- end -%>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section--articles-travel bg-orange text-blue-dark px-4" id="destination-inspiration">
  <div class="container mx-auto xl:px-32 xxl:px-48 pt-12 pb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-10">Destination inspiration</h2>
    <p class="text-xl xl:text-3xl mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-tight">Be inspired by these stories of overland travel. If you have a story of flight-free travel to share, please <a href="mailto:info@flightfree.co.uk" class="underline underline-blue hover:text-blue">get in touch</a>.</p>
    <%= partial "articles", locals: { articles: blog.articles } %>
  </div>
</section>

</main>
